| Login error displayed on wrong credentials | TC-T3.2 |
| Register auto-logins | TC-T3.3 |
| Logout clears all state | TC-T3.4 |
| Token validation on mount | TC-T3.5, TC-T3.6 |
| authFetch adds Bearer header | TC-T3.7 |
| 401 response clears auth | TC-T3.8 |
| isAdmin computed | TC-T3.9, TC-T3.10 |

